{"tid":1396921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工根本唔洗擔心有手尾","createTime":"2019-08-02T09:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:56:37.000Z","uid":261478,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4420d47a6a443aa46589731564172d1ca7aaf660","tid":1396921,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:05:36.000Z","msg":"罷工係你基本嘅權利<br />\n勞工法寫明罷工唔算曠工<br />\n老細無權因為你罷工而炒你<br />\n再者當公司有一半人罷工<br />\n老細都無可能全部炒晒<br />\n炒晒間公司根本無可能run到<br />\n再者如果老細揪後算帳嘅一定比人起底杯割<br />\n要驚嘅唔係你而係你老細<br />\n所以唔好再講咩怕比人揪後算帳而仆住去返工<br />\n香港大家都有份<br />\n前線義士為左香港做左咁多<br />\n罷工咁低成本又有效都唔做嘅<br />\n根本唔佩做香港人<br />\n<br />\n覺得我講得啱就幫推<br />\n等多d人見到<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e66dd4a24762d4dba556c3a480faeef61e5d5754","tid":1396921,"uid":282624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"啱聽<br />\n罷佢老母"},{"pid":"6bddfb14cfd2af10d386cb8983c4cbaed2d51d0b","tid":1396921,"uid":237425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家要玩估領袖MODE</span><br />\n唔好有人帶頭搞手<br />\n就唔會有人針對比人搞而槍打出頭<br />\n大家不動聲色就奈唔到你地何<br />\n<br />\n光復香港! 時代革命!"},{"pid":"543eb5dd0a44bd373e9b179320d92f2c2e1e727b","tid":1396921,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2e2a6a262724acf33e26903bc1682039b18fc58e","tid":1396921,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8bac8191e75c3f226c3f60a8a5d9a20a031b4828","tid":1396921,"uid":261232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"956acc0fb959ed547fe321de3ab0e14cf84d0012","tid":1396921,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:01:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"618df3b9abc388bfc331d5327193bdd13c794192","tid":1396921,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201